{"id":505,"ayahs":[{"number":21,"arabic":"۞ وَٱذْكُرْ أَخَا عَادٍ إِذْ أَنذَرَ قَوْمَهُۥ بِٱلْأَحْقَافِ وَقَدْ خَلَتِ ٱلنُّذُرُ مِنۢ بَيْنِ يَدَيْهِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِهِۦٓ أَلَّا تَعْبُدُوٓا۟ إِلَّا ٱللَّهَ إِنِّىٓ أَخَافُ عَلَيْكُمْ عَذَابَ يَوْمٍ عَظِيمٍۢ","translation":"AND REMEMBER that brother of [the tribe of] Ad, how - seeing that [other] warnings had already come and gone within his own knowledge as well as in times beyond his ken - he warned his people [who lived] among those sand-dunes: “Worship none but God! Verily, I fear lest suffering befall you on an awesome day!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4531.mp3","surahId":46,"words":[{"id":23559,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَٱذْكُرْ","translation":"এবং স্মরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23560,"position":2,"arabic":"أَخَا","translation":"ভাই","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23561,"position":3,"arabic":"عَادٍ","translation":"আ'দের (অর্থাৎ হুদের কথা)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23562,"position":4,"arabic":"إِذْ","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23563,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنذَرَ","translation":"সে সতর্ক করেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23564,"position":6,"arabic":"قَوْمَهُۥ","translation":"তার জাতিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23565,"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱلْأَحْقَافِ","translation":"আহকাফ (উপত্যকায়)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23566,"position":8,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23567,"position":9,"arabic":"خَلَتِ","translation":"অতীত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23568,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلنُّذُرُ","translation":"সতর্ককারীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23569,"position":11,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23570,"position":12,"arabic":"بَيْنِ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23571,"position":13,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"তার নিকট অতীতেও","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23572,"position":14,"arabic":"وَمِنْ","translation":"এবং","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23573,"position":15,"arabic":"خَلْفِهِۦٓ","translation":"তার পরেও (এই বলে)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23574,"position":16,"arabic":"أَلَّا","translation":"\"যে না","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23575,"position":17,"arabic":"تَعْبُدُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা এবাদত করো (অন্য কারো)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23576,"position":18,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"ব্যতীত","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23577,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23578,"position":20,"arabic":"إِنِّىٓ","translation":"আমি নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23579,"position":21,"arabic":"أَخَافُ","translation":"ভয় করি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23580,"position":22,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23581,"position":23,"arabic":"عَذَابَ","translation":"শাস্তির","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23582,"position":24,"arabic":"يَوْمٍ","translation":"(এমন এক) দিনের","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23583,"position":25,"arabic":"عَظِيمٍۢ","translation":"(যা) বড় কঠিন\"","audioUrl":"wbw/046_021_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23584,"position":26,"arabic":"٢١","translation":"(২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":22,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟ أَجِئْتَنَا لِتَأْفِكَنَا عَنْ ءَالِهَتِنَا فَأْتِنَا بِمَا تَعِدُنَآ إِن كُنتَ مِنَ ٱلصَّٰدِقِينَ","translation":"They answered: “Hast thou come to seduce us away from our gods? Bring, then, upon us that [doom] with which thou threaten us, if thou art a man of truth!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4532.mp3","surahId":46,"words":[{"id":24589,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24590,"position":2,"arabic":"أَجِئْتَنَا","translation":"\"তুমি আমাদের কাছে এসেছ কি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24591,"position":3,"arabic":"لِتَأْفِكَنَا","translation":"আমাদেরকে ফিরাবে তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24592,"position":4,"arabic":"عَنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24593,"position":5,"arabic":"ءَالِهَتِنَا","translation":"আমাদের উপাস্যগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24594,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأْتِنَا","translation":"আমাদের কাছে আন তাহলে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24595,"position":7,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয় নিয়ে যার","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24596,"position":8,"arabic":"تَعِدُنَآ","translation":"তুমি আমাদেরকে ভয় দেখাচ্ছ","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24597,"position":9,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24598,"position":10,"arabic":"كُنتَ","translation":"তুমি হও","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24599,"position":11,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"অন্তর্ভুক্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24600,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰدِقِينَ","translation":"সত্যবাদীদের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/046_022_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24601,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٢","translation":"(২২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":23,"arabic":"قَالَ إِنَّمَا ٱلْعِلْمُ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَأُبَلِّغُكُم مَّآ أُرْسِلْتُ بِهِۦ وَلَٰكِنِّىٓ أَرَىٰكُمْ قَوْمًۭا تَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"Said he: “Knowledge [of when it is to befall you] rests with God alone: I but convey unto you the message with which I have been entrusted; but I see that you are people ignorant [of right and wrong]!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4533.mp3","surahId":46,"words":[{"id":25671,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25672,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"\"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25673,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْعِلْمُ","translation":"এ জ্ঞান (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25674,"position":4,"arabic":"عِندَ","translation":"(শুধুমাত্র) নিকট","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25675,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহরই","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25676,"position":6,"arabic":"وَأُبَلِّغُكُم","translation":"এবং আমি তোমাদের পৌঁছাই","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25677,"position":7,"arabic":"مَّآ","translation":"সেই (পয়গাম)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25678,"position":8,"arabic":"أُرْسِلْتُ","translation":"আমি প্রেরিত হয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25679,"position":9,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"যা নিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25680,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنِّىٓ","translation":"কিন্তু আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25681,"position":11,"arabic":"أَرَىٰكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে দেখছি","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25682,"position":12,"arabic":"قَوْمًۭا","translation":"(এমন) লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25683,"position":13,"arabic":"تَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"(যারা) মূর্খতা করছ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/046_023_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25684,"position":14,"arabic":"٢٣","translation":"(২৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":24,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا رَأَوْهُ عَارِضًۭا مُّسْتَقْبِلَ أَوْدِيَتِهِمْ قَالُوا۟ هَٰذَا عَارِضٌۭ مُّمْطِرُنَا ۚ بَلْ هُوَ مَا ٱسْتَعْجَلْتُم بِهِۦ ۖ رِيحٌۭ فِيهَا عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"And so, when they beheld it in the shape of a dense cloud approaching their valleys, they exclaimed, “This is but a heavy cloud which will bring us [wel­come] rain!” [But Hud said:] “Nay, but it is the very thing which you [so contemptuously] sought to hasten - a wind bearing grievous suffering,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4534.mp3","surahId":46,"words":[{"id":26740,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26741,"position":2,"arabic":"رَأَوْهُ","translation":"তারা তা দেখলো","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26742,"position":3,"arabic":"عَارِضًۭا","translation":"মেঘমালারূপে","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26743,"position":4,"arabic":"مُّسْتَقْبِلَ","translation":"আগ্রসরমান","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26744,"position":5,"arabic":"أَوْدِيَتِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের উপত্যকাগুলোর (দিকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26745,"position":6,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26746,"position":7,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","translation":"\"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26747,"position":8,"arabic":"عَارِضٌۭ","translation":"মেঘমালা","audioUrl":"wbw/046_024_008.mp3",